metadata.name: Dans le Bus
metadata.description:
The Eiffel Tower photographed through tempered glass from inside a tour bus driving to Versailles, Paris, 2014.

As a gift to myself for my 45th birthday I traveled to Paris with esteemed commercial photographer Joe Baraban for his Springtime in Paris photo workshop and fell in LOVE with the City! The images in this collection are all from this 10 day period, many of which have never been exhibited or released for public viewing.

Location  
Paris

Date of Capture: May 28, 2014
